title: Roger This - Owl Right
description:
Track List 

1. This One Goes to Eleven
2. Fly With the Seabirds
3. Hazze
4. This is My Nightmare
5. Indie and the Jones
6. Easier Sad Than Dumb
7. One Big Jump


Chicago south-side natives, Roger This, bring you their sophomore EP "Owl Right". Following their 2013 debut release "All We Need of Hell" the boys are stepping up the game and are mixing in even more genres, tones, emotions, and attitude than ever before. From relaxed surf punk-like songs about human equality like "Fly With the Seabirds" to disdain filled, relationship inspired punk-rock tunes like "Easier Sad Than Dumb" to the smooth blues rock sounds of "Haze", Roger This is sure to keep you ears' attention and take you on a musical endeavor like you never embarked on before, owl right?
